msgctxt "Addon Description"
msgid "Universal Scraper is currently the most customizable scraper by collecting information from the following supported sites: IMDb, TMDb, Rotten Tomatoes, Trakt.tv, OFDb.de, port.hu. This scraper is currently the flagship of the Team-XBMC scrapers. The initial search can be done either on TMDb or IMDb (according to the settings), but following that it can be set field by field that from which site you want that specific information."
msgstr "本刮削器从以下站点获取信息：IMDb、TMDb、Rotten Tomatoes、Trakt.tv、OFDb.de。初始结果总是先从TMDb获取，然后可以针对不同项目分别设置从不同站点获取信息。"
